Package: easyNRD
Title: Tidy Tools for HCUP Nationwide Readmissions Database Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ali", "Salman", email = "alisalman.et.al@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tidy, out-of-core framework for Healthcare Cost and
    Utilization Project Nationwide Readmissions Database (HCUP-NRD) data.
    Built on 'arrow' and 'duckdb', 'easyNRD' provides a composable pipeline to
    ingest raw files, consolidate transfer-linked hospitalizations into
    clinical episodes, and link index events to first qualifying readmissions.
    The workflow preserves denominator integrity and supports statistically
    robust survival and competing-risk analyses without exhausting system
    memory.
